Output echo-tool.gif
Set Theme "Catppuccin Macchiato"

Set Shell zsh
Sleep 1.5s
Type "echo Hello world!"
Enter
Sleep 3s
Ctrl+L
Type "./xcuecho Hello world!"
Sleep 1s
Enter
Sleep 3s
Ctrl+L
Type "./xcuecho Hello world! -a"
Sleep 1s
Enter
Sleep 3s
Ctrl+L
Type "./xcuecho Hello world! -u"
Sleep 1s
Enter
Sleep 3s
Ctrl+L
Type "./xcuecho Hello world! -l"
Sleep 1s
Enter
Sleep 5s
